OL,3,CWriter of Mr Bates v The Post Office
OL,4,Csays more people are asking her for
OL,5,Chelp
OL,7,FThe popular ITV series opened the
OL,8,Ffloodgates for people who share a
OL,9,Fsimilar experience of authority doing
OL,10,Fthem wrong. Many of them are now
OL,11,Fcontacting Ms Hughes for help.
OL,13,FThey are sharing their own terrible
OL,14,Fexperiences, wondering if she can turn
OL,15,Fher writing skills to their
OL,16,Fpredicament and help in the same way
OL,17,FMr Bates brought the Horizon scandal
OL,18,Fback into the public consciousness.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/9
