OL,3,CWriter of Mr Bates v The Post Office
OL,4,Csays more people are asking her for
OL,5,Chelp
OL,7,FThe power of Mr Bates v The Post
OL,8,FOffice has led to much musing on the
OL,9,Fpower of drama as a whole, Ms Hughes
OL,10,Fsays, adding that she is proud the
OL,11,Fgenre is once more having a moment.
OL,13,F"Drama can just reach in and grab you,
OL,14,Fin a way that politicians might
OL,15,Fstruggle," she says.
OL,17,FMs Hughes deserves every accolade for
OL,18,Fher work on the series.
