OL,3,CWriter of Mr Bates v The Post Office
OL,4,Csays more people are asking her for
OL,5,Chelp
OL,7,FWhen producers first approached her
OL,8,Fwith the story, she agreed to write it
OL,9,Fwithout really knowing many details.
OL,11,FBut she is passionate about writing
OL,12,Fabout ordinary people, all the better
OL,13,Fif they are from the North - she lives
OL,14,Fin North Yorkshire and says she
OL,15,Factively seeks ways of putting the
OL,16,Fstories of Northerners on screen.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/9
