OL,7,FIt is little wonder then that the
OL,8,Fseries had such an impact on the
OL,9,Fviewers.
OL,11,FOf course, this is not the first drama
OL,12,Fseries Ms Hughes has worked on.
OL,14,FShe has a history in costume dramas,
OL,15,Flike the magnificent 2018 Apple TV
OL,16,Fseries Vanity Fair. She is
OL,17,Fdisappointed that the genre is out of
OL,18,Ffashion right now.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/9
