OL,7,FMs Hughes is also acutely aware of the
OL,8,Fneed to keep the Post Office victims'
OL,9,Fexperiences in the headlines as they
OL,10,Fseek compensation and justice in its
OL,11,Ftotality.
OL,13,FBut few can deny that Ms Hughes - a
OL,14,Fgentle, unassuming, but fiercely
OL,15,Fcommitted writer - has taken a
OL,16,Fsignificant step for those victims,
OL,17,Fthough she says what has happened
OL,18,Fsince, is far beyond what anyone could
OL,19,Fhave expected.
